programme.title: The Big Interview: Andoni Iraola
programme.desc: Having arrived on these shores to manage Bournemouth in 2023, Andoni Iraola took over a club which had narrowly avoided relegation. Today, they are considered one of the toughest sides to play against in the Premier League. With exclusive access, this week the Bournemouth manager gives the Big Interview a guided tour of some of the local spots he likes to visit on the Dorset coastline. Iraola opens up on growing up in Spain, playing alongside Xabi Alonso and Mikel Arteta, how his footballing philosophy is turning Bournemouth’s fortunes around and what he loves most about the place he now calls home.(n)
